ls|ss|ls|sh|ls|sd|ls|sc|nt|Obviously one deal doesn't prove anything, but on this deal 3NT looks like a better contract than 4@H (as would usually be the case when both hands are 4333). My personal style is that I rarely bid Stayman when I am 4333, but there are plenty of very successful players who would disagree with my opinions in this area. |
